keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map k scrollDown
map K scrollPageDown
map i scrollUp
map I scrollPageUp
map J goBack
map L goForward

unmap p
unmap c
unmap r
unmap t
unmap oc
unmap x
unmap v
unmap b
